metadata.name: Consciousness
metadata.description:
It is a collection of individuals, moreover, one whole being

It depends on how you approach it, how you see


When you close up and stare

When you look away and in wide view

When observed in lucid will

When taken visually as a vague landscape

It is regular and irregular writhing

It is collective and independent


How it is reflected is up to you

-------

This work is based on digital, but all frames are drawn by hand.
